title: New Nogizaka Star Tanjou!
overview: So far, they have challenged themselves with "wandering travel" in "Nogizaka Doko e" and "comedy" in "Nogizaka Skits". The fourth generation, who are the future of Nogizaka46. The next challenge for these girls is... Showa era songs! They will sing covers of hit songs from the past! They'll also perform serious duets with big-name male singers!
